title: Superman 3 Extended TV Version
description:
This is the extended TV version of Superman 3. It is taken from a PAL VHS recorded in the 80s so the quality is not fantastic but it is well watchable and pretty good really for the age of the tape. It was recorded from Yorkshire Television (ITV) in the UK. 

It is 2 hours 13 mins in length and is in 4:3 PAL DVD format (720x576i, 25fps).

Includes the 'Space' opening, 'Smallville Flash' scene, 'Hairdryer' line etc
